FBIS4-63162 "drsov098_s_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-098 Daily Report 19 May 1994 Georgia Defense Ministry Foreign Relations Department Head Named Defense Ministry Foreign Relations Department Head Named LD1905174594 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1330 GMT 19 May 94 LD1905174594 Tbilisi IBERIA Georgian BFN [Text] Tbilisi, 19 May -- The press service of the Georgian Defense Ministry has informed Iberia news agency that, at the order of Georgian Defense Minister Lieutenant General Vardiko Nadibaidze, Colonel Davit Tevzadze, who is the holder of the Vakhtang Gorgasali Order 1st Degree, has been appointed head of the Defense Ministry's Foreign Relations Department. Before the appointment to this post, Col. Tevzadze worked as head of brigade No. 11. Col. Tevzadze is a full member of the New York Academy of Sciences. He is married with four children.
